{
  "stem": "25639.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was sort of a futile type of process, because there was nothing that they were building with this, that I could tell.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this was a much smaller camp than Auschwitz, as I could tell.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So that-- that was it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was in Bergen-Belsen for a short time, and from there I was shipped out in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we arrived in the industrial city of Braunschweig.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there we were housed in the-- in the barn of the horses of the SS.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But there were rings along the side wall-- along one side of the wall of this barn-- long, long barn.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it was also located in the midst of a residential area.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that's where we were housed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The horses were taken out and tied to these rings outside, and we slept on the concrete floor.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "About 600 to 800 of us performed slave labor in Braunschweig.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We slept on the floor, which had some damp and moldy straw-- well, on it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And in the mornings we were counted off, and taken to our job site.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the-- in this barn, they provided for us by creating-- by slashing a hole through the cement floor, which became our latrine.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In one corner of the barn was-- in a triangle shape-- was the housing of the SS kommandant-- a female kommandant.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I believe that her name was Hermina Braunsteiner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A woman SS.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she had sort of a dirty blonde hair, and a very bad [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] permanent.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was fuzzy hair.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she wore a-- a black cape, and had always a whip in her hand.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she was vicious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she had a dog.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
